# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Closed / large research data — MUST NOT enter the public (Zenodo) archive.
# The domain runs (labour market, physics ensemble) depend on Rosstat data and
# the python_solver / python_forecast packages, which are not redistributable.
# Keep only the self-contained numpy core + synthetic reproduction in git.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.npy
*.npz
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.pkl
*.pickle
*.parquet
*.feather
/data/
/raw/
/private/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Generated figure images (regenerated by figures/make_figures.py).
# Uncomment if you prefer to ship rendered figures inside the DOI archive.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# figures/*.png
# figures/*.pdf
# figures/*.svg

# Note: small provenance artefacts are intentionally TRACKED, not ignored —
# experiments/*.csv (phase-map grids) and experiments/timing.log.
